DISCRETIONARY APPEALS ALLOWED

98-952. Biddle v. Warren Gen. Hosp.

TrumlWl App. No. 96-T-5582. On appeal of Robert L. Holland and Elliott, Heller, Maas, Moro & Magill Co. and on appeal of Warren General Hospital and Kevin Andrews. Discretionary appeals allowed.

On cross-appeal of Cheryl A. Biddle et al. Discretionary cross-appeal allowed.

Cook, J., would allow Propositions of Law Nos. III through VII only on the cross-appeal.
